## 4.订单详情
/order/detail.do

http://localhost:8088/order/detail.do?orderNo=1480515829406
>  request
>> orderNo


> response
>>  fail
```json
{
  "status": 1,
  "msg": "没有找到订单"
}
```
  success
```json
{
  "status": 0,
  "data": {
    "orderNo": 1480515829406,
    "payment": 30000.00,
    "paymentType": 1,
    "paymentTypeDesc": "在线支付",
    "postage": 0,
    "status": 10,
    "statusDesc": "未支付",
    "paymentTime": "",
    "sendTime": "",
    "endTime": "",
    "closeTime": "",
