## 5.取消订单
/order/cancel.do

http://localhost:8088/cart/select.do?productId=1
>  request
>> orderNo


> response
>>  fail
```json
{
  "status": 1,
  "msg": "该用户没有此订单"
}
```
或
```json
{
  "status": 1,
  "msg": "此订单已付款，无法被取消"
}
```
  success
```json
{
  "status": 0
}
```
